moos-ivp-uav-base
=================

This repository contains MOOS-IvP applications, behaviors, and missions for
ArduPilot fixed-wing and multicopter UAVs.

The maintained project overview and documentation links are in README.md.
The canonical pArduBridge documentation starts at:

  wiki/pArduBridge/INDEX.md

Build from the repository root with:

  ./build.sh

Add this repository's bin directory to PATH and its lib directory to
IVP_BEHAVIOR_DIRS before launching missions.
